data.description: This updated 3-bedroom, 2-full bath Cape Cod offers the perfect blend of style and convenience, featuring an inviting open-concept layout, fenced rear yard with a deck for entertaining and a covered wrap-around porch. Don't forget about the great location! You have walkability to a nearby coffee shop, easy access to Bender Mountain Walking Trail, Fernbank Park, golf courses, dining and so much more! Easy access to the highway, downtown Cincinnati, Northern Kentucky and the airport. Added touches include a versatile playroom or office space, new LVT flooring, updated kitchen with white cabinetry and counter bar, all appliances stay, renovated 1st floor bath, new windows & doors, new gutter system, updated landscaping, pathways, walkways & more! Total square feet is 1,895
